data.description: Introducing a charming 1-story house nestled in the serene city of Elmendorf. This inviting home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering both comfort and convenience for everyday living. Step inside and be captivated by the stunning interior finish out that sets this property apart. The carefully designed layout maximizes space while creating an atmosphere of warmth and modern elegance. Gleaming vinyl plank floors throughout, seamlessly connecting each room. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring sleek countertops, ample cabinet space, and top-of-the-line appliances that make meal preparation a delight. Whether you're hosting gatherings or enjoying quiet evenings, the open-concept living area provides a versatile space to relax and entertain. The spacious bedrooms offer a peaceful retreat, each with its own unique charm. The master suite is a true haven, complete with an ensuite bathroom that exudes luxury. From the custom tiling to the modern fixtures, every detail has been carefully chosen to enhance your daily routine. One of the standout features of this property is its enviable location within a community that doesn't have an HOA. This means you can enjoy your space with the freedom to personalize it according to your preferences. The lack of an HOA fee adds to the appeal, making this home a rare find in today's market. Elmendorf's tranquil ambiance provides a welcome escape from the bustle of the city, while still being conveniently close to essential amenities. Nearby parks, schools, and shopping centers offer a myriad of options for recreation and daily needs. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or seeking to downsize, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Elmendorf beauty your forever home.
